INSERT INTO `feature_page_sections` VALUES (1,1,'Pameran Kontemporer \"Aceh Merekam Zaman\"','Contemporary Exhibition \"Aceh Recording the Times\"','Pada Ruang depan lobby tamu BAST terdapat Panel Pameran Sejarah tentang Aceh yang bertajuk \"Aceh Merekam Zaman\"\r\nberisikan panel tentang Identitas Para Pahwalan \"Patriot Tanah Rencong\" yang telah diakui oleh NKRI, terdapat panel yang berisi tentang susana di Aceh pada masa lampau, serta panel yang berisikan foto foto \"Pesona Serambi Makkah\" diharapkan dengan adanya pameran tersebut dapat membuat pengunjung merasa lebih nyaman untuk beristirahat sambil melihat konten pameran tersebut .','In the front room of the BAST guest lobby there is a historical exhibition panel about Aceh entitled \"Aceh Recording the Era\"\r\ncontains a panel about the Identity of the Pahwalan \"Patriot Tanah Rencong\" which has been recognized by the Republic of Indonesia, there is a panel containing about the atmosphere in Aceh in the past, as well as a panel containing photos of \"Pesona Serambi Makkah\" it is hoped that this exhibition can make visitors feel more comfortable to rest while viewing the contents of the exhibition.','[\"features/sections/HZydWEm26Zq6v5J7UAAfo2lmgEK0Ps0nbukqVkah.jpg\", \"features/sections/uQnd98btu3ageA5USTT1QhDFrAVYdcL3CyIAbO4k.jpg\", \"features/sections/UT1FjprbFm2MhrDKb3iWXlTDXyx6eoot5d7Gb6tr.jpg\", \"features/sections/QBuNzJGzDa9XSdsmwQqFZlra5EUVxCnVFaT9uZSw.jpg\", \"features/sections/g047KpSTMBkvEYnNG03GhYz1ks2PR9OrBmMKXUye.jpg\"]','[\"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\"]',1,'2026-03-10 21:16:09','2026-04-22 04:46:08'),(3,1,'Fasilitas Mini Diorama Pameran Arsip','Archives Exhibition Mini Diorama Facilities','Balai Arsip Statis dan Tsunami (BAST) membentuk Pusat Studi Arsip Kebencanaan/Arsip Tsunami sebagaimana disebutkan dalam Keputusan Kepala Arsip Nasional Republik Indonesia Nomor 424 Tahun 2021 Tentang Pusat Studi Arsip Kebencanaan/Arsip Tsunami\r\nPusat Studi ini akan menjadi rujukan sumber informasi yang autentik dan terpercaya bagi para peneliti yang ingin memanfaatkan arsip-arsip tsunami yang tersimpan di Balai Arsip Statis dan Tsunami.\r\nDalam hal tersebut untuk menarik minat pengunung dalam meneliti arsip pasca tsunami dengan ini BAST akan menampilkan pameran kontemporer bertajuk \"17 Tahun Refleksi Aceh dan Nias Pasca Gempa Bumi dan Tsunami\" pada tahun 2021\r\nPameran tersebut berisi  Panel Merawat Harapan Pasca Bencana,  Panel Miniatur 3D Kapal Korban Tsunami,  Panel Perubahan Daratan Tsunami, serta  TV Interaktif pemutaran Video Tsunami','The Center for Static and Tsunami Archives (BAST) established the Disaster Archives/Tsunami Archives Study Center as stated in the Decree of the Head of the National Archives of the Republic of Indonesia Number 424 of 2021 concerning the Disaster Archives/Tsunami Archives Study Center\r\nThis Study Center will be a reference source for authentic and trusted information for researchers who want to utilize the tsunami archives stored at the Static and Tsunami Archives Center.\r\nIn this regard, to attract the interest of visitors in researching post-tsunami archives, BAST will present a contemporary exhibition entitled \"17 Years of Reflections on Aceh and Nias after the Earthquake and Tsunami\" in 2021\r\nThe exhibition contains a panel on Caring for Post-Disaster Hope, a 3D Miniature Panel of Tsunami Victim Ships, a Panel on Changes in Tsunami Land, as well as an Interactive TV showing Tsunami Videos.','[\"features/sections/8lH7mwg78er1a9Gs7A607YsbPQ3UtbrzPngXVh3g.jpg\", \"features/sections/nqTWQLwgEwKLiEvE37veWyV18TbO6BY6RWtSJ0oS.jpg\", \"features/sections/ZGZQwNx9kPeLZ0mWEKrbcl8gRkje60VPZ9oe1rAP.jpg\", \"features/sections/uhkdPCWHaV99QXgXVa5dTg81cuMvcalQYAMHgSPr.jpg\", \"features/sections/BadsN190xXIRkreelLZRNMNTKaWKIwsFsAxf58VY.jpg\"]','[\"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\"]',2,'2026-03-10 21:32:14','2026-04-22 04:46:41'),(8,17,'Fasilitas Mini Theater Film','Mini Theater Film Facilities','Fasilitas Mini Theater untuk pemutaran film dokumenter pasca tsunami bagi pengunjung yang ingin menonton film tersebut selayaknya di biokop\r\ndengan dukungan layar Smart tv 85\" serta Sound system yang memadai, Mini Theater ini dapat menampung hingga 30 Peserta dalam satu sesi..','Mini Theater facilities for screening post-tsunami documentary films for visitors who want to watch the film like in a cinema\r\nWith the support of an 85\" Smart TV screen and an adequate sound system, this Mini Theater can accommodate up to 30 participants in one session.','[\"features/sections/TiOXOPV9ivpH8sMYhssCayjq4Uk5BdsS7wGTxiqi.jpg\", \"features/sections/3lLBb0D2Ov7QO5zjibVuVP9GEQC73JMd4S6iGoeW.jpg\", \"features/sections/obnfmZnheXQBNoD8BbjdaklC7SvsD1akR0wYoAgi.jpg\", \"features/sections/NM70JC1xDqk3P6vUmLVXZpOdm94ULgjmbmXalk6d.jpg\", \"features/sections/dv5KhI7kvJ45jDD55dgsnBeNVmItsVPFXnXOILBh.jpg\"]','[\"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\"]',1,'2026-04-22 04:59:04','2026-04-22 04:59:04'),(9,17,'Pameran Arsip Kebencanaan/Arsip Tsunami','Disaster Archives/Tsunami Archives Exhibition','Dalam rangka memperingati 19 tahun gempa dan tsunami Aceh,  Balai Arsip Statis dan Tsunami (BAST) Arsip Nasional Republik Indonesia (ANRI) menyelenggarakan pameran arsip kebencanaan/arsip tsunami yang merupakan salah satu dari rangkaian kegiatan dalam puncak acara peringatan 19 tahun gempa dan tsunami Aceh, B19 Wave to Learn : Belajar Tsunami dari Arsip.\r\n\r\nPameran tersebut mengambil beberapa tema diantaranya Eksistensi Perempuan Aceh dalam Rehabilitasi dan Rekonstruksi serta Ketangguhan Perempuan Indonesia pada Masa Perjuangan Kemerdekaan RI. Kedua tema ini diambil sebagai bentuk penghargaan bagi perempuan di seluruh Indonesia dalam perjuangannya untuk bangkit melawan kesulitan, tidak peduli seberat apa pun kehidupan yang telah dilaluinya.\r\n\r\nSelain itu, BAST turut menampilkan pameran bertemakan Tapak Demi Tapak Mengubah Air Mata Menjadi Mata Air yang menampilkan kolase perjalanan BAST dalam menjalankan tugas memberikan manfaatnya kepada masyarakat luas.\r\n\r\nMelalui pameran arsip kebencanaan/arsip tsunami ini diharapkan dapat menambah pembelajaran dan wawasan terkait arsip kebencanaan, serta dapat menjadi bahan renungan bahwa bencana tidak selamanya tentang duka, ada banyak hal yang dapat dipetik dalam perjalanan kehidupan, di hari ini maupun di hari esok yang akan datang.','In commemoration of the 19th anniversary of the Aceh earthquake and tsunami, the Static and Tsunami Archives Center (BAST) of the National Archives of the Republic of Indonesia (ANRI) held an exhibition of disaster archives/tsunami archives which was one of a series of activities at the peak of the event commemorating the 19th anniversary of the Aceh earthquake and tsunami, B19 Wave to Learn: Learning about the Tsunami from the Archives.\r\n\r\nThe exhibition has several themes, including the existence of Acehnese women in rehabilitation and reconstruction and the resilience of Indonesian women during the struggle for Indonesian independence. These two themes were taken as a form of appreciation for women throughout Indonesia in their struggle to rise above adversity, no matter how difficult life has been.\r\n\r\nApart from that, BAST also displayed an exhibition with the theme Tapak by Tapak Changing Tears into Springs which displayed a collage of BAST\'s journey in carrying out its duties of providing benefits to the wider community.\r\n\r\nThrough this exhibition of disaster archives/tsunami archives, it is hoped that it can increase learning and insight regarding disaster archives, and can become material for reflection that disasters are not always about sorrow, there are many things that can be learned in the journey of life, today and in the future.','[\"features/sections/OK2K3KkXUTBHwHsp0JHGNMLqAA0HwxIQRLALRNRj.jpg\", \"features/sections/Rp1xaslzdBvbw4fw4B6HpJHvAR1q3sXXIQok7Yai.jpg\", \"features/sections/llE1J9MiRHSEULih3xgcpLMekLodC0RqtouJsOTI.jpg\", \"features/sections/o79Sj1IkPwM6OSb8SupfIH3dEVU9Zlo6Ak87xrZi.jpg\", \"features/sections/hsMbGoMoEoUKYaga0D5dogFo7CiGbI8Bry1AINWM.jpg\"]','[\"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\", \"50% 50%\"]',2,'2026-04-22 05:00:37','2026-04-22 05:02:00');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `feature_page_sections` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

